0.9921 Sun Apr 14 2013
    - Fix 2.9.4 handling of wxConnection::Execute

0.9919 Sat Apr 13 2013
    - Makefile checks for supported Wx version
    - Fixed wxUSE_DATAVIEWCTRL constant ( rt#84566 )
